column16: Adron Chambers grounds into a force out, shortstop Jed Lowrie to second baseman Jose Altuve.    Shane Robinson out at 2nd.
Shane Robinson singles on a ground ball to right fielder Chris Johnson.    Steven Hill to 2nd.
Tyler Greene flies out to center fielder Justin Maxwell.
Steven Hill reaches on fielding error by first baseman Chris Snyder.
David Freese homers (12) on a fly ball to left field.   Allen Craig scores.
Allen Craig singles on a line drive to left fielder J.  D.   Martinez.
Matt Adams flies out to center fielder Justin Maxwell.
